---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---
<PageLayout
  title="Membership"
  description="Free teaches you to create. Premium teaches you to monetize and systematize. VIP buys back your time."
>
  <div class="page-eyebrow">The Digital Income Edit™</div>
  <h1>Membership</h1>
  <p class="lede">Free teaches you to create. Premium teaches you to monetize. VIP buys back your time.</p>

  <p>The membership grows with you, one rung at a time — no leaps, no overwhelm. You climb when the current step stops being your bottleneck.</p>

  <div style="border-top:1px solid var(--gray);margin-top:40px">
    <div style="padding:26px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray)">
      <div style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px">Free</div>
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;color:var(--taupe-deep)">Start-here trainings, daily prompts, and the free community. Your first win, fast.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="padding:26px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray)">
      <div style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px">Premium — $9/mo</div>
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;color:var(--taupe-deep)">Learn to monetize and systematize — including the PLR Vault™ and full content, offer, and funnel training.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="padding:26px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray)">
      <div style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px">VIP</div>
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;color:var(--taupe-deep)">Done-for-you assets, monthly content calendars, and scaling systems. Buy back your time.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a class="btn" href="https://www.skool.com/thedigitalincomeedit/plans?utm_campaign=skool_link_sidebar_links&utm_content=84529be4ccf6404fbd5b7235626ae55d" style="margin-top:40px">Join the Membership <span class="a">→</span></a>

  <p style="margin-top:60px"><a href="/learn" style="color:var(--pink);font-weight:500">← Back to The Library</a></p>
</PageLayout>
